      </ul>
      <p>Class diagram, Dataschema (ERD), Use case diagram, Mock-ups zijn verwerkt in het technisch ontwerp.</p>
    `,
      docs: [{
        pdf: '/doc/Onderbouwing_1.pdf',
        buttons: ['Class diagram', 'Dataschema', 'Use case diagram', 'Mock-up'],
        images: ['/images/Onderbouwing1_ClassDiagram.png', '/images/Onderbouwing1_Dataschema.png', '/images/Onderbouwing1_UseCaseDiagram.png', '/images/Onderbouwing1_Mockup.png']
